{"tid":1632961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《禁止蒙面規例》實施後首次有人被控　兩男女今提堂","createTime":"2019-10-07T01:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T01:59:37.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8f1d39533ffdfd57f40beea4b0bedc81c80257c8","tid":1632961,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:26:46.000Z","msg":"《禁止蒙面規例》上星期六實施後，首次有人被控，今日提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方上星期六凌晨在藍田啟田道，發現有人非法集結及用雜物設置路障，企圖堵塞馬路，警員在現場拘捕一名18歲男子及一名38歲女子，兩人被暫控合共一項「非法集結」及各一項違反《禁止蒙面規例》罪，今日在東區裁判法院提堂。"},{"pid":"3d4789158b5052ad4ae376e02fb502f54dd3c5da","tid":1632961,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:57:26.000Z","msg":"兩人非法集結？"},{"pid":"49623424e18e0529c3f948f37dce1a2251cd8f6a","tid":1632961,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:59:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji